n orders issued</p></td><td><p>5592</p></td><td><p>6425</p></td><td><p>6268</p></td><td><p>6401</p></td><td><p>6043</p></td><td><p>5926</p></td><td><p>5900</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","South Holland and The Deepings","Mr John Hayes","36216","2016-05-10T10:19:30.42Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/517203/answer","Biography information for Sir John Hayes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/517203/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/517203/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2016-05-03","Proceeds of Crime","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what the value was of assets (a) subject to restraint orders and (b) recovered using confiscation orders under the Proceeds of Crime Act 2002 in each year since 2009-10.","false","Biography information for Tulip Siddiq","Hampstead and Kilburn","Tulip Siddiq","36215"
